videos.headline: Illinois' Gay blocks USF field goal
videos.description: Isaiah Gay blocks Emilio Nadelman kick to keep the game knotted at 0-0.

videos.headline: Flowers connects with Antoine for a TD
videos.description: Quinton Flowers completes a pass to Deangelo Antoine for a 39-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Illinois picks up two points on a blocked extra point
videos.description: After South Florida scores a touchdown, kicker Emilio Nadelman's extra point is blocked and returned to the house by Illinois for two points.

videos.headline: Senat ejected for the second time in 3 games
videos.description: Deadrin Senat gets tossed for targeting for his hit on Illinois' QB Chayce Crouch.

videos.headline: Adams intercepts Flowers' pass in the end zone
videos.description: Quinton Flowers' pass is picked off in the end zone by Tony Adams for a touchback.

videos.headline: Flowers to Valdes-Scantling puts USF in the red zone
videos.description: Quinton Flowers links up with Marquez Valdes-Scantling for a 43-yard pass putting the Bulls in the red zone.

videos.headline: Tice runs in for a 10-yard TD
videos.description: Darius Tice rushes for 10 yards and a touchdown to extend South Florida's lead in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Illinois RB breaks free for a 45-yard TD
videos.description: Mike Epstein runs for a 45-yard touchdown late in the second quarter to close in on South Florida.

videos.headline: South Florida runs for TD as time expires
videos.description: Quinton flowers's 6-yard run puts South Florida up 23-9 at the half.

videos.headline: Valdes-Scantling gets his second TD of the night
videos.description: Quinton Flowers finds Marquez Valdes-Scantling for a 17-yard TD to extend the Bulls' lead.

videos.headline: Green tossed for targeting
videos.description: Stanley Green is thrown out of the game for helmet -to-helmet hit on Darius Tice.

videos.headline: Flowers finds Johnson for a TD
videos.description: Quinton Flowers connects with D'Ernest Johnson for a 17-yard touchdown to extend the Bulls' lead.

videos.headline: George Jr. pulls in a 21-yard TD
videos.description: Mike Epstein completes to Jeff George Jr. for a 21-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: McCants extends South Florida's lead with a TD
videos.description: Quinton Flowers finds Tyre McCants for a 13-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.
